<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <%= render :partial => 'layouts/head_tags' %>
  <body id="homepage">
    <header class="homepage-top one" data-removeclass='one'>
      <div class="container">
        <ul class="homepage-menu nav navbar-nav">
          <% if current_user && current_user.admin? %>
            <%= render :partial => 'layouts/admin_links' %>
          <% elsif current_user && current_user.agent? %>
            <%= render :partial => 'layouts/agent_links' %>
          <% elsif current_user %>
            <%= render :partial => 'layouts/user_links' %>
          <% else %>
            <%= render :partial => 'layouts/public_links' %>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-sm-4'>
            <div class='homepage-logo-responsive visible-xs'>
              <%= image_tag 'mi_logo_white.png', class: 'img-responsive' %>
            </div>
            <div class='homepage-image-text hidden-xs gray-background'>
              The Easiest Way to Document Your Personal Belongings
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='col-sm-6'>
            <div class='homepage-logo hidden-xs'>
              <%= link_to image_tag('mi_logo_white.png'), root_path %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="green lead text-center">
      <div class="container">
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-md-8 col-md-offset-2'>
            <h2 style="color:black;">Your Shield of Protection for Peace of Mind...</h2>
            <p>Having a personal inventory can help you bounce back from a disaster, fire, flood, burglary, or anything else that might compromise your belongings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class='white lead'>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 text-center'>
            <p>
              The wildfires in Arizona, California and other states, floods and or other disaster, prove just how important it is to have a home inventory right at your fingertips. The cost to protect your personal belongings is minimal compared to what you stand to lose. 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row home-small">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="well home-well">
              <b>
                Your up to date personal inventory can help you:
              </b>
              <ul>
                <li>Settle insurance claims faster</li>
                <li>Assist with estate planning, divorce settlement, etc.</li>
                <li>Determine appropriate levels of coverage</li>
                <li>Validate the value of your personal belongings</li>
                <li>Substantiate losses for your income tax return</li>
                <li>Insurance recommended</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="well home-well">
              <b>
                Inventorying your personal possessions using My Inventory LLC is:
              </b>
              <ul>
                <li>Safe, secure and confidential</li>
                <li>Affordable</li>
                <li>A streamlined process</li>
                <li>Accessible anytime, anywhere and from any device</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='text-center btn-row'>
          <%= link_to 'Learn More', services_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="homepage-main gray">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-4 homepage-block">
            <p>
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-cloud"></span>
            </p>
            <p class="head">Cloud Based</p>
            <p class="body">Inventories are created and stored online.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4 homepage-block">
            <p>
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock"></span>
            </p>
            <p class="head">Secure</p>
            <p class="body">Your information is safe and secure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4 homepage-block">
            <p>
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-envelope"></span>
            </p>
            <p class="head">Share</p>
            <p class="body">Share your inventory with a few clicks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class='white lead text-center'>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-md-8 col-md-offset-2'>
            <p>
              Your up to date personal inventory can help you settle insurance claims faster, determine appropriate levels of coverage, or substantiate losses for your income tax return. You may need extra coverage for jewelry, furs, and collectibles.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='text-center btn-row'>
          <%= link_to 'Get Started', signup_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class='gray lead'>
      <div class="container">
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-md-6 text-center'>
            <p>
              Create, access, and update<br />your inventory from any device.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-6'>
            <%= image_tag 'devices.png', class: 'img-responsive image-center' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="green lead">
      <div class="container">
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-md-6'>
            MyInventory works in two ways:<br />
            1. Have a MI agent complete your inventory.<br />
            2. Complete an inventory on your own.<br />
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-6'>
            Easy to Use Tools:
            <div class='row'>
              <div class='col-sm-6'>
                <p>
                  Upload Images<br />
                  Include Comments<br />
                  Email Report<br />
                  Helpful Tutorials<br />
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class='col-sm-6'>
                <p>
                  Custom Items<br />
                  PDF Report<br />
                  Room by Room<br />
                  And More<br />
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='row'>

          <div class='col-sm-12'>
            <div class='text-center btn-row'>
              <%= link_to 'Get Started', signup_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

	<%= render :partial => 'layouts/footer' %>

  </body>
</html>
